# transposeTriangle

- _transposeTriangle(t)_

Transpose the triangular array _t_.

Transpose a 4×4 upper left triangular array:

```
>>> [
>>> 	11 13 10 7;
>>> 	24 23 17;
>>> 	34 30;
>>> 	41
>>> ].transposeTriangle
[
	11 24 34 41;
	13 23 30;
	10 17;
	7
]
```

* * *

See also: transpose, transposeIrregular, transposeTableau

Guides: Array Functions
